    == image_tag "../images/recipes/buttermilk-pancakes.jpg", class:"recipe-image recipe-image--hero"
    h1.recipe-title Perfect buttermilk pancakes
    .recipe-intro
      p I have tried a lot of different pancake recipes over the years. Breakfast (or brunch) is my favourite meal of the day and pancakes, in every shape and form, are always a solid choice.
      p These buttermilk ones are quite different to the thinner plate-covering Dutch discs I grew up with, but I honestly can't say which ones I prefer anymore.

    ul.recipe-info
      li.recipe-info__item
        ' Takes:
        strong 10 mins
      li.recipe-info__item
        ' Serves:
        strong 4
      li.recipe-info__item
